block.description: Get Conversation Members in Workbot for Slack (Custom)

data.channel:
=if _('data.logger.e7fc39f4.message')[_('data.foreach.4019e59c.index', 'foreach_meta')] == "#venom"
lookup("SLACK_VARIABLES", key: "slack.venom.channelId")["value"]
elsif _('data.logger.e7fc39f4.message')[_('data.foreach.4019e59c.index', 'foreach_meta')] == "#dr-doom"
lookup("SLACK_VARIABLES", key: "slack.dr-doom.channelId")["value"]
else
lookup("SLACK_VARIABLES", key: "slack.loki.channelId")["value"]
end
